---
---
<section id="approach" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-black text-accent tracking-[0.3em] uppercase opacity-90">OPERATIONAL_GUIDELINES //</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-outfit text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">Battle-Tested.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="h-px flex-grow bg-white/10"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 border border-white/10">
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-white/10 hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors group relative">
      <div class="corner-marker marker-tl w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div class="text-accent mono text-[10px] font-black mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">[01] ARCHITECTURE</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 font-outfit text-white uppercase tracking-tight">Simple Ships First</h3>
      <p class="text-mute text-base leading-relaxed font-medium">
        The simplest stack that gets the job done. No resume-driven complexity, no frameworks 
        I can't defend, no infrastructure that isn't earning its keep.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="p-10 border-r border-white/10 hover:bg-accent/5 transition-colors group relative">
      <div class="corner-marker marker-tl w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div class="text-accent mono text-[10px] font-black mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">[02] PROCESS</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 font-outfit text-white uppercase tracking-tight">SPEC_THEN_CODE</h3>
      <p class="text-white text-base leading-relaxed font-black">
        Every feature starts with a spec: what you're building and how you'll know it works. 
        Then code. Then polish. The order matters.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="p-10 hover:bg-cyan-500/[0.02] transition-colors group relative">
      <div class="corner-marker marker-tl w-4 h-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div class="text-cyan-500 mono text-[10px] font-black mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">[03] BIAS</div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 font-outfit text-white uppercase tracking-tight">EDGE_FIRST_BIAS</h3>
      <p class="text-mute text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
        Systems that run on your own hardware, with your own data. Keys on disk,
        code on GitHub, nothing phoning home.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
